    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[使用Hexo + NexT搭建静态博客]]></title>
      <url>/2017/07/02/hexo-build/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本站使用 Hexo 来搭建，使用 NexT 主题，这里记录一下搭建本站的整个过程，仅供参考。</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h1 id="1-环境准备"><a href="#1-环境准备" class="headerlink" title="1. 环境准备"></a>1. 环境准备</h1><p>下载安装 Node.js 和 Git(for windows) ，我的搭建环境是 win10-64bit</p>
<h2 id="1-1-Node-js安装"><a href="#1-1-Node-js安装" class="headerlink" title="1.1. Node.js安装"></a>1.1. Node.js安装</h2><p>官网下载地址：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://nodejs.org/en/</a> 下载 v* LTS Recommended For Most Users</p>
<h3 id="1-1-1-设置环境变量"><a href="#1-1-1-设置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="1.1.1 设置环境变量"></a>1.1.1 设置环境变量</h3><p>安装 Node.js,并设置环境变量 Path 的值为相应的安装路径，我是装在了 D 盘的 nodejs 目录下</p>
<h3 id="1-1-2-安装-Express-开发框架"><a href="#1-1-2-安装-Express-开发框架" class="headerlink" title="1.1.2 安装 Express 开发框架"></a>1.1.2 安装 Express 开发框架</h3><p>打开 CMD 命令窗口，执行命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install -g express</div><div class="line">npm install -g express-generator</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>若生成了 express 和 express-generator 两个文件夹，则表示安装好了</p>
<h3 id="1-1-3-新建项目"><a href="#1-1-3-新建项目" class="headerlink" title="1.1.3 新建项目"></a>1.1.3 新建项目</h3><p>进入 Node.js 目录下，新建名称为 newproject 的项目</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> D:\nodejs</div><div class="line">express -t ejs newproject</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>若新建成功，则在 nodejs 目录下会生成 newproject 目录，其目录大致包括以下文件</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">bin          相关运行脚本</div><div class="line">public       静态资源</div><div class="line">routes       路由表</div><div class="line">views        视图文件夹</div><div class="line">app.js       视图模板</div><div class="line">packge.json  项目依赖说明</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="1-1-4-安装模块"><a href="#1-1-4-安装模块" class="headerlink" title="1.1.4 安装模块"></a>1.1.4 安装模块</h3><p>进入 newproject 目录下, 安装模块</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> newsproject</div><div class="line">npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="1-1-5-启动项目"><a href="#1-1-5-启动项目" class="headerlink" title="1.1.5 启动项目"></a>1.1.5 启动项目</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm start</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在浏览器访问 <a href="http://localhost:3000/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:3000/</a> 若测试出现页面 Welcome to Express ，表示 Node.js 安装成功，并可以正常部署项目</p>
<p>可输入以下命令查看版本号</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">node -v</div><div class="line">npm -v</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="1-2-Git安装"><a href="#1-2-Git安装" class="headerlink" title="1.2 Git安装"></a>1.2 Git安装</h2><p>官网下载地址：<a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://nodejs.org/en/</a>，具体安装很简单不多说了</p>
<h1 id="2-安装-Hexo"><a href="#2-安装-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装 Hexo"></a>2. 安装 Hexo</h1><h2 id="2-1-安装-Hexo"><a href="#2-1-安装-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="2.1 安装 Hexo"></a>2.1 安装 Hexo</h2><p>Git 安装成功后，打开命令窗口，进入到桌面目录下，执行命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm -g hexo-cli  <span class="comment"># g代表全局，npm默认为当前项目安装</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 D 盘新建 blog 文件夹，这个文件夹就是博客的根目录，进入 blog 目录下。</p>
<h2 id="2-2-Hexo-初始化和安装依赖包"><a href="#2-2-Hexo-初始化和安装依赖包" class="headerlink" title="2.2 Hexo 初始化和安装依赖包"></a>2.2 Hexo 初始化和安装依赖包</h2><p>首先对 blog 文件夹进行 hexo 初始化和安装依赖包</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo init</div><div class="line">npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>之后会生成一些文件</p>
<h2 id="2-3-生成静态资源"><a href="#2-3-生成静态资源" class="headerlink" title="2.3 生成静态资源"></a>2.3 生成静态资源</h2><p>生成 public 文件夹（浏览器访问资源）</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo g</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="2-4-启动服务"><a href="#2-4-启动服务" class="headerlink" title="2.4 启动服务"></a>2.4 启动服务</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo s</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在浏览器访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:4000/</a> 便可查看 Hexo 默认的主题</p>
<h2 id="2-5-下载-NexT-主题"><a href="#2-5-下载-NexT-主题" class="headerlink" title="2.5 下载 NexT 主题"></a>2.5 下载 NexT 主题</h2><p>在 blog 根目录下执行命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> http://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>clone 完成后进入 blog/themes 目录下就能看到两个主题，一个是默认的，一个是 NexT 主题</p>
<h2 id="2-6-配置-NexT-主题"><a href="#2-6-配置-NexT-主题" class="headerlink" title="2.6 配置 NexT 主题"></a>2.6 配置 NexT 主题</h2><p>站点配置文件： D:\blog_config.yml<br>主题配置文件： D:\blog\themes\next_config.yml</p>
<p>在站点配置文件中搜素 “theme” ，设置该值为 next ，需要注意的是冒号后面有一个空格</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Extensions</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># theme: landscape</span></div><div class="line">theme: next</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 blog 目录下分别执行清除静态资源，生成静态资源，启动服务命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo clean</div><div class="line">hexo g</div><div class="line">hexo s</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在浏览器中访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:4000/</a> 便可看到效果</p>
<p>在主题配置文件搜索 “scheme” ，如下所示有三种方案可选，只需要将 # 去掉就可以了</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Schemes</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># scheme: Muse</span></div><div class="line">scheme: Mist</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Pisces</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此时，本地资源基本上完成了</p>
<h1 id="3-添加功能"><a href="#3-添加功能" class="headerlink" title="3. 添加功能"></a>3. 添加功能</h1><h2 id="3-1-设置语言"><a href="#3-1-设置语言" class="headerlink" title="3.1 设置语言"></a>3.1 设置语言</h2><p>在主题配置文件中搜索 “language” ，设置该值为 zh-Hans</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">language: zh-Hans</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这样就引用了 themes\next\languages\zh-Hans.yml 文件，打开这个文件就可以看到每个 key 对应的都是中文字体</p>
<h2 id="3-2-标签和分类"><a href="#3-2-标签和分类" class="headerlink" title="3.2 标签和分类"></a>3.2 标签和分类</h2><p>在主题配置文件中搜索 “menu” ，如果想隐藏菜单栏中的某个选项只要在前面加上 # 即可</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">menu:</div><div class="line">  home: /</div><div class="line">  categories: /categories/  <span class="comment"># 分类</span></div><div class="line">  archives: /archives/  <span class="comment">#归档</span></div><div class="line">  tags: /tags/  <span class="comment"># 标签</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="comment">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404.html</span></div><div class="line">  about: /about/  <span class="comment"># 关于</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此处将 categories 和 tags 设为显示</p>
<p>在 blog 目录下执行一下命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo n page <span class="string">"categories"</span></div><div class="line">hexo n page <span class="string">"tags"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此时会生成 source\categories 和 source\tags 两个文件夹，里面都有 index.md 文件，修改内容为</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">---</div><div class="line">title: categories</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">type</span>: categories</div><div class="line">---</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">---</div><div class="line">title: tags</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">type</span>: tags</div><div class="line">---</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>再使用命令生成博文文件</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo n <span class="string">"name"</span>  <span class="comment"># name 文章全称</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>生成文章时，在对应的 name.md 中可以这样添加标签和分类</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">---</div><div class="line">title: 使用Hexo + NexT搭建静态博客</div><div class="line">date: 2017-07-02 23:50:37</div><div class="line">update: 2017-07-09 16:19:11</div><div class="line">categories: Hexo             <span class="comment"># 分类</span></div><div class="line">tags: [Node.js, Hexo, NexT]   <span class="comment"># [标签1, 标签2..., 标签n]</span></div><div class="line">---</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-3-新增留言功能"><a href="#3-3-新增留言功能" class="headerlink" title="3.3 新增留言功能"></a>3.3 新增留言功能</h2><p>在主题配置文件搜索 “menu” ，添加 message</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">menu:</div><div class="line">  home: /</div><div class="line">  categories: /categories/  <span class="comment"># 分类</span></div><div class="line">  archives: /archives/  <span class="comment">#归档</span></div><div class="line">  tags: /tags/  <span class="comment"># 标签</span></div><div class="line">  message: /message <span class="comment"># 留言</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="comment">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404.html</span></div><div class="line">  about: /about/  <span class="comment"># 关于</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>搜索 “menu_icons” 配置图标</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">menu_icons:</div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="comment">#KeyMapsToMenuItemKey: NameOfTheIconFromFontAwesome</span></div><div class="line">  home: home</div><div class="line">  categories: th</div><div class="line">  <span class="comment"># schedule: calendar</span></div><div class="line">  tags: tags</div><div class="line">  archives: archive</div><div class="line">  <span class="comment"># sitemap: sitemap</span></div><div class="line">  commonweal: heartbeat</div><div class="line">  message: external-link</div><div class="line">  about: user</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在 themes\next\languages\zh-Hans.yml 文件添加留言选项以配置对应的中文名称</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">menu:</div><div class="line">  home: 首页</div><div class="line">  archives: 归档</div><div class="line">  categories: 分类</div><div class="line">  tags: 标签</div><div class="line">  about: 关于</div><div class="line">  search: 搜索</div><div class="line">  message: 留言            <span class="comment"># 新增 留言</span></div><div class="line">  commonweal: 公益404</div><div class="line">  udpate: 更新</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后执行命令</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo n page <span class="string">"message"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>重新清除，生成和启动便可看到效果，只不过目前留言功能什么都没有</p>
<h2 id="3-4-修改头像"><a href="#3-4-修改头像" class="headerlink" title="3.4 修改头像"></a>3.4 修改头像</h2><p>把头像 0.jpg 图片放在 themes\next\source\images 目录下</p>
<p>在站点配置文件中修改字段 avatar</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置头像</span></div><div class="line">avatar: /images/0.jpg</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-5-侧边栏社交链接"><a href="#3-5-侧边栏社交链接" class="headerlink" title="3.5 侧边栏社交链接"></a>3.5 侧边栏社交链接</h2><p>侧边栏社交链接的修改包含两个部分，一个是链接，一个是链接图标，两者均在主题配置文件中</p>
<p>链接放置在 social 字段下，一行一个链接。其键值格式是 显示文本: 链接地址</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Social links</span></div><div class="line">social:</div><div class="line">  GitHub: https://github.com/your-user-name</div><div class="line">  Twitter: https://twitter.com/your-user-name</div><div class="line">  微博: http://weibo.com/your-user-name</div><div class="line">  豆瓣: http://douban.com/people/your-user-name</div><div class="line">  知乎: http://www.zhihu.com/people/your-user-name</div><div class="line">  <span class="comment"># 等等</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>设定链接的图标，对应的字段是 social_icons 。其键值格式是 匹配值: 图标名称，匹配键与上一步所配置的链接的显示文本相同（大小写严格匹配）， enable 选项用于控制是否显示图标</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Social Icons</span></div><div class="line">social_icons:</div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="comment"># Icon Mappings</span></div><div class="line">  GitHub: github</div><div class="line">  Twitter: twitter</div><div class="line">  微博: weibo</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-6-友情链接"><a href="#3-6-友情链接" class="headerlink" title="3.6 友情链接"></a>3.6 友情链接</h2><p>在主题配置文件中添加</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Blogrolls</span></div><div class="line">links_title: 友情链接</div><div class="line">links_layout: inline</div><div class="line">links_icon: link  <span class="comment"># 设置图标</span></div><div class="line">links:</div><div class="line">  一百度: http://www.baidu.com/</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-7-文章配置"><a href="#3-7-文章配置" class="headerlink" title="3.7 文章配置"></a>3.7 文章配置</h2><h3 id="3-7-1-开启阅读全文"><a href="#3-7-1-开启阅读全文" class="headerlink" title="3.7.1 开启阅读全文"></a>3.7.1 开启阅读全文</h3><p>方法1：在文章中进行截断（推荐使用），以下给出文章 md 文件片段内容</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">---</div><div class="line">title: Hello World</div><div class="line">date: 2017-07-02 16:48:38</div><div class="line">categories: 日记  <span class="comment"># 分类</span></div><div class="line">tags: 日记</div><div class="line">---</div><div class="line">未被截断内容，会在主页中显示</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;  <span class="comment"># 直接在文章的 md 文件中添加 &lt;!-- more --&gt; 标注即可</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">以下为被截断的内容</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>方法2：修改主题配置文件</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">auto_excerpt:</div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>  <span class="comment"># 开启文章阅全文</span></div><div class="line">  length: 2000   <span class="comment"># 显示长度</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="3-7-2-为文章增加打赏"><a href="#3-7-2-为文章增加打赏" class="headerlink" title="3.7.2 为文章增加打赏"></a>3.7.2 为文章增加打赏</h3><p>修改主题配置文件，收款二维码放在 themes\next\source\images 目录下</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Donate 文章末尾显示打赏按钮</span></div><div class="line">reward_comment: 如果文章对您有用请随意打赏，谢谢支持！</div><div class="line">wechatpay: /images/w.png</div><div class="line">alipay: /images/z.jpg</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="3-7-3-设置代码高亮主题"><a href="#3-7-3-设置代码高亮主题" class="headerlink" title="3.7.3 设置代码高亮主题"></a>3.7.3 设置代码高亮主题</h3><p>NexT 使用 Tomorrow Theme 作为代码高亮，共有5款主题可选择。 NexT 默认使用白色的 normal 主题，可选的值有 normal，night，night blue，night bright，night eighties 。在主题配置文件中修改</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Code Highlight theme</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Available value:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">#    normal | night | night eighties | night blue | night bright</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># https://github.com/chriskempson/tomorrow-theme</span></div><div class="line">highlight_theme: night eighties       <span class="comment"># 修改即可</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="3-7-4-文章添加音乐链接"><a href="#3-7-4-文章添加音乐链接" class="headerlink" title="3.7.4 文章添加音乐链接"></a>3.7.4 文章添加音乐链接</h3><p>Hexo 支持解析 markdown 语法，因此每篇博文都是以 .md 结尾的文件。而 markdown 又支持如表格、脚注、内嵌 HTML 等，所以在 .md 文件中直接添加 HTML 代码</p>
<p>网易云音乐、虾米音乐都可以生成内嵌音乐的 HTML 代码，复制粘贴到 .md文件中即可</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;center&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;iframe frameborder=<span class="string">"no"</span> border=<span class="string">"0"</span> marginwidth=<span class="string">"0"</span> marginheight=<span class="string">"0"</span> width=330 height=86</div><div class="line">			src=<span class="string">"https://music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=33856282&amp;auto=0&amp;height=66"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/iframe&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;/center&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-8-统计站点访问次数"><a href="#3-8-统计站点访问次数" class="headerlink" title="3.8 统计站点访问次数"></a>3.8 统计站点访问次数</h2><p>修改 themes/next/layout/_partials 目录下的 footer.swig</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;div class=<span class="string">"theme-info"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">  &#123;&#123; __(<span class="string">'footer.theme'</span>) &#125;&#125; -</div><div class="line">  &lt;a class=<span class="string">"theme-link"</span> href=<span class="string">"https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">    NexT.&#123;&#123; theme.scheme &#125;&#125;</div><div class="line">  &lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">&#123;<span class="comment"># 新增代码 #&#125;</span></div><div class="line">&lt;script async src=<span class="string">"https://dn-lbstatics.qbox.me/busuanzi/2.3/busuanzi.pure.mini.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;div style=<span class="string">"margin:-20px;position: absolute;right:265px;"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;dl style=<span class="string">"float:left"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">  &lt;dt style=<span class="string">"float:left"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;dd style=<span class="string">"float:left;width:300px"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">      &lt;span style=<span class="string">"float:right"</span>&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;|&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">      &lt;span style=<span class="string">"float:right"</span>&gt;本站总访问量&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=<span class="string">"float:right"</span> id=<span class="string">"busuanzi_value_site_pv"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/dd&gt;</div><div class="line">  &lt;/dt&gt;</div><div class="line">  &lt;dt style=<span class="string">"float:left;width:300px"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;dd&gt;</div><div class="line">      &lt;span style=<span class="string">"float:left"</span>&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">      &lt;span style=<span class="string">"float:left"</span>&gt;您是第&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">      &lt;span style=<span class="string">"float:left"</span> id=<span class="string">"busuanzi_value_site_uv"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">      &lt;span style=<span class="string">"float:left"</span>&gt;个小伙伴&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">    &lt;/dd&gt;</div><div class="line">  &lt;/dt&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/dl&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">&#123;<span class="comment"># 结束 #&#125;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-9-本地站内搜索"><a href="#3-9-本地站内搜索" class="headerlink" title="3.9 本地站内搜索"></a>3.9 本地站内搜索</h2><p>安装 hexo-generator-search ，在站点的根目录下执行以下命令:</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>编辑站点配置文件，新增以下内容到任意位置</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">search:</div><div class="line">  path: search.xml</div><div class="line">  field: post</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-10-统计本站运行天数"><a href="#3-10-统计本站运行天数" class="headerlink" title="3.10 统计本站运行天数"></a>3.10 统计本站运行天数</h2><p>修改 blog\themes\next\layout_partials\footer.swig 文件，在后面追加以下代码</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;script&gt;</div><div class="line">	var birthDay = new Date(<span class="string">'07/02/2017'</span>);</div><div class="line">	var now = new Date();</div><div class="line">	var duration = now.getTime() - birthDay.getTime();</div><div class="line">	var total= Math.floor(duration / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));</div><div class="line">	document.getElementById(<span class="string">'showDays'</span>).innerHTML=<span class="string">'本站已运行'</span> + total + <span class="string">'天'</span>;</div><div class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在最后一个 div 中追加一下代码</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;span id=<span class="string">"showDays"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="4-博客项目托管到-Github"><a href="#4-博客项目托管到-Github" class="headerlink" title="4. 博客项目托管到 Github"></a>4. 博客项目托管到 Github</h1><h2 id="4-1-创建-Repository"><a href="#4-1-创建-Repository" class="headerlink" title="4.1 创建 Repository"></a>4.1 创建 Repository</h2><p>注册 Github 账号，网址：<a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/</a></p>
<p>点击 New 创建新的 Repository ，以我的为例：</p>
<p>Owner: shifengl</p>
<p>Repository name: shifengl.github.io</p>
<p>勾选 Initialize the repository with a README</p>
<p>点击 Create repository</p>
<h2 id="4-2-修改站点配置文件"><a href="#4-2-修改站点配置文件" class="headerlink" title="4.2 修改站点配置文件"></a>4.2 修改站点配置文件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></div><div class="line">deploy:</div><div class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</div><div class="line">  repository: git@github.com:shifengl/shifengl.github.io.git</div><div class="line">  branch: master</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="4-3-配置-sshkey"><a href="#4-3-配置-sshkey" class="headerlink" title="4.3 配置 sshkey"></a>4.3 配置 sshkey</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"注册git的邮箱"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>连续按几个回车，密码为空，然后在 C:\Users\Administrator.ssh 下，得到两个文件 id_rsa 和 id_rsa.pub</p>
<p>若出现问题，应该是原本已存在 Github 的sshkey，请自行搜索解决方案清除后重试</p>
<h2 id="4-4-Github-上添加-SSH-密钥"><a href="#4-4-Github-上添加-SSH-密钥" class="headerlink" title="4.4 Github 上添加 SSH 密钥"></a>4.4 Github 上添加 SSH 密钥</h2><p>打开 <a href="https://github.com/setting/ssh" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/setting/ssh</a> new SSH key 添加密钥，title 随便写，key 则为 id_rsa.pub 所有内容</p>
<h2 id="4-5-验证是否能链接到-Github"><a href="#4-5-验证是否能链接到-Github" class="headerlink" title="4.5 验证是否能链接到 Github"></a>4.5 验证是否能链接到 Github</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>如果提示</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">The authenticity of host <span class="string">'github.com (192.30.253.112)'</span> can<span class="string">'t be established.</span></div><div class="line">RSA key fingerprint is SHA256:nThbg6kXUpJWGl7E1IGOCspRomTxdCARLviKw6E5SY8.</div><div class="line">Are you sure you want to continue connecting (yes/no)? y</div><div class="line">Please type 'yes<span class="string">' or '</span>no<span class="string">': yes</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>或者提示覆盖原来的文件，选择 yes 回车，只要能看到如下提示就能成功连接到github</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">Hi zhangsan! You<span class="string">'ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>以后会继续探索更多功能！</p>
]]></content>
      
        
